comments: Nurkic (POR) brings his left hand forward and releases away to roll without applying any force as marginal contact occurs with LeVert's (CLE) side during the pick.
Nurkic (POR) grasps and then quickly releases Allen's (CLE) left arm during rebounding.
Hart (POR) and Mitchell (CLE) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm/body contact occurs during the rebound.
Mobley (CLE) gathers the pass on his left foot and takes two steps before elevating for the dunk attempt.
Simons (POR) brings his left hand forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Mobley's (CLE) right side as he elevates for the dunk attempt.
LeVert (CLE) and Lillard (POR) come together at the same spot inside the perimeter and LeVert absorbs the marginal body contact.
LeVert (CLE) brings his hands toward Lillard's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs with Lillard's left side at the end of the drive.
Mitchell (CLE) is turning alongside Hart's (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs prior to Mitchell cleanly dislodging the ball away.
Hart (POR) inbounds the ball within five seconds.

Nurkic (POR) continues to re-establish his screening position following the initial contact with Garland (CLE) and he initiates further contact with Garland's side/lower body as Garland attempts to go over.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Grant's (POR) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
LeVert (CLE) cleanly back-taps the ball prior to incidental arm/body contact occurring with Lillard (POR) during the rebound.
Hart (POR) moves forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Mitchell's (CLE) back/side as Mitchell receives the pass.
Nurkic (POR) and Simons (POR) legally contest Mitchell's (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Allen (CLE) is retreating toward the baseline while in a vertical defensive position and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs during Lillard's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) establishes his left foot as his pivot and lifts/re-plants it at the start of his dribble.
Nurkic (POR) initiates contact across Mobley's (CLE) right arm and causes Mobley to lose control of the ball.
Hart (POR) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
LeVert (CLE) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Hart (POR) raises his right arm up as he pursues the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Mitchell's (CLE) right hand/wrist.
